  "body": "### Description\nAs a private network operator, I want an option that minimizes unexpected confusion by setting sensible defaults. I want my profile to handle my use-case specifically. \n\n### Acceptance Criteria\nThe profile implements the following defaults\n- Sync-mode: FAST (move to snap â€”> not until snap server and Bonsai are tested in this environment, might require bonsai archive for some networks to migrate entirely over)\n- `--fast-sync-min-peers=3` (`--sync-min-peers` #6327)\n- `--remote-connections-limit-enabled=false`\n- Tx-pool=Legacy / Sequential\n    - `--tx-pool-no-local-priority` \n    - `--tx-pool-limit-by-account-percentage=`(something bigger than 4 transactions)\n",
